data.title: Youth Teams latest – Wellington AFC
data.text:
In addition to our thriving youth set-up of 30 teams, we hold the following weekly sessions for boys and girls.

Details are as follows:

Ages three to five years – Saturdays (11.15am to 12 noon) at the Playing Field.

All-girl coaching sessions – Thursday evenings. During the season in the sports hall at Court Fields School – 5.30pm to 6.30pm for under 11s; on the Wellington School Astro – 7pm for 8pm for over 11s. During the summer at Court Fields School – 5.30pm to 8.30pm depending on age group.
